OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779393955
OL,3,CDuck saved from pipe at water
OL,4,Ctreatment in Liverpool
OL,6,FThe RSPCA released the bird into a
OL,7,Fcanal.
OL,9,FA duck has been rescued from a United
OL,10,FUtilities water treatment works pipe
OL,11,Fin Liverpool.
OL,13,FThe RSPCA responded after a volunteer
OL,14,Freported the bird stuck and in
OL,15,Fdistress at the bottom of the pipe in
OL,16,FHope Carr Terrance at Leigh on May 14.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
