PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779393955
OL,3,CDuck saved from pipe at water
OL,4,Ctreatment in Liverpool
OL,6,FThe female duck was lifted to safety
OL,7,Fwith a net attached to a search and
OL,8,Frescue pole, she was uninjured and
OL,9,Freleased onto the Leeds and Liverpool
OL,10,Fcanal.
OL,12,FRSPCA deputy chief inspector Jess
OL,13,FPierce said, "This poor duck was stuck
OL,14,Ftight and unable to spread her wings
OL,15,For move about, six to seven feet down
OL,16,Fa narrow pipe.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779393955
OL,3,CDuck saved from pipe at water
OL,4,Ctreatment in Liverpool
OL,6,F"We don't know how she got in there
OL,7,Fbut she had probably been there for 24
OL,8,Fhours, so it was fortunate that she
OL,9,Fwas spotted as the pipe was partly
OL,10,Fobscured under a stretch of metal
OL,11,Fgrid."
OL,13,FJess continued, "It took us a while to
OL,14,Ffind her as we drew a blank at another
OL,15,FUnited Utilities water treatment site
OL,16,Fnearby at Trafford Way in Urmston.
OL,26,@uD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
