OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779393955
OL,3,CDuck saved from pipe at water
OL,4,Ctreatment in Liverpool
OL,6,F"We only had a video to go on as a
OL,7,Fstaff member had reported it
OL,8,Fanonymously. Eventually, we were able
OL,9,Fto match that up with the pipe at the
OL,10,FLeigh works where the duck was trapped
OL,11,Fand carry out the rescue."
OL,13,FThere is advice on how to help trapped
OL,14,Fbirds at the RSPCA website.
